Package: lab-guardian
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9), python3-pip, python3-psutil, python3-requests
Maintainer: Lab Insight Team <labinsight@example.com>
Description: Lab Guardian — Student monitoring agent
 Lightweight Python agent that reports running processes,
 connected devices and network information to the Lab Insight
 backend via WebSocket.
